lead_paragraph: Liverpool striker Divock Origi has found it "very difficult" to cope with his lack of involvement in Juergen Klopp's preferred line-up but insists he has worked on other aspects of his game to be ready when his chance arises.

headline.print_headline: Origi Hopes to Learn From Tough Spell on Liverpool Bench
headline.main: Origi Hopes to Learn From Tough Spell on Liverpool Bench
